item.title: Prayer bpn10246 in Māori
item.description: E Koe Te Atua Parakore Kaha Rawa! E Koe tōku Ariki ngākau māhaki! Tukua mai ki ahau te kaha e āhei ai ahau ki te karo i ngā tūkino o ngā iwi me ngā hūāngatanga o te ao. Hōmai ki ahau te kaha e āhei ai ngā ngaru o aku ngana kia rite ki te tae o Te Moananui-a-Kiwa, ki ngā tahatika o te Rāwhiti o te Uru hoki. (Source category: KARAKIA MŌ TE MOANANUIA-KIWA) (Bahaiprayers.
